snippet.title: Solaria - Wake Up With The Wolves (Live At Whisky a Go Go in 2011)
snippet.description:
Siegfried Song Facebook : http://www.facebook.com/SiegfriedSongOfficial

In 2011, a band asked for a video of my performance for an audition. But at that time, there was no video contains my performance. So for the shoot, me and my friends planned a show, and first we had to write new vocal melodies and lyrics. But since I was in middle of semester, I had little time to prepare. On the day of the performance, the song was not completed, and we went on stage without practicing properly. And we made TONS of mistakes. I was so ashamed of the show then I didn't reveal this video to anyone. From then on, I was obsessed with perfectionism and was too harsh on myself, and I wasn't happy at all while doing music stuff that I loved. By releasing this video today, I am trying to forgive my immature but proud past.

If you like this song despite my mistakes, I'll make a recorded version of it again! So please leave a few comments and share with your friends!

Solaria - Wake Up With The Wolves (Live At Whisky a Go Go in 2011)

Siegfried Song (Symmetric Chaos, South Korea) - Lead Vocals
Alex Nasla (Witherfall, USA) - Keyboards
Devin Reich (Anubis, USA) - Lead Guitars and Rhythm Guitars
Adam Nasla (Solaria, USA) - Rhythm Guitars
Mariano Baglietto (Solaria, Peru) - Bass
Chris Mitsch-Meyering (Solaria, USA) - Drums
